text.section:
All nonelected city offices shall be created by ordinance which shall specify:
Title of office;
Powers and duties of office;
Oath of office; and
Bond, if required.

A city may create nonelected offices other than those referred to in this subsection. For purposes of the requirements of this section, the following shall be considered nonelected offices:
City clerk;
City manager;
City administrator;
Chief of police; and
Fire chief, other than a volunteer fire chief.
